    "description": "《伏魔天师》是一款融合了角色性格及Roguelike玩法的卡牌构筑类游戏，玩家在一个神鬼莫测的世界中偶遇一系列的妖魔鬼怪，可做法驱妖、可锄强扶弱、也可逃之夭夭，玩家面对妖魔鬼怪可选择各种策略，每一次的抉择也将改变自身的性格，随着性格变化后续遇到的人和事也将随之改变。<br>在这世界你想扮演的是力量为尊的杀戮者、慈悲为怀的和善者、孤高的叛逆者、亦或正义的守序者全由您自己抉择，您每一次的抉择都将重塑自我性格，随着性格变化不仅仅影响卡牌获取，也将影响一次次的奇遇事件；<br>游戏特色<br>构建自己的性格<br>通过开局先天资质、每次怪物的抉择都将改变自己的性格构成，一个好的性格构成，往往能加速你的卡组构成；<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114500/extras/86cc7002d719f90d0450defac8583c1c.poster.avif?t=1669818932\" width=726 height=408 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114500/extras/86cc7002d719f90d0450defac8583c1c.webm?t=1669818932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114500/extras/86cc7002d719f90d0450defac8583c1c.mp4?t=1669818932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>指定的性格考验<br>当你某项性格成长到一定值时，将遇到不同阶段的性格考验，你可选择放弃考验或接受考验，若能通过考验你将得到前所未有的成长；<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114500/extras/10fa2d57fb348970a68c5b0df85e0a3d.poster.avif?t=1669818932\" width=726 height=408 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114500/extras/10fa2d57fb348970a68c5b0df85e0a3d.webm?t=1669818932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114500/extras/10fa2d57fb348970a68c5b0df85e0a3d.mp4?t=1669818932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>构建极致的牌组<br>通过不断完善自己的性格构成，加速牌组构建，不断的历练，不断取舍，决定哪些卡牌加入你的牌组，最终构成极致的牌组，打出完美的套路流；<br>让你在窥视怪物的特性后，完全沉浸在组牌、出牌的乐趣中；<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114500/extras/9663ea08dd1a4fcef76b99f5ffb48fde.poster.avif?t=1669818932\" width=726 height=408 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114500/extras/9663ea08dd1a4fcef76b99f5ffb48fde.webm?t=1669818932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114500/extras/9663ea08dd1a4fcef76b99f5ffb48fde.mp4?t=1669818932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>特色怪物<br>在这神鬼莫测的世界中，你将遇到形形色色的妖魔鬼怪，各种魅惑、诅咒、治愈、枷锁、同生共死各种能力千奇百怪。充分了解怪物特性，根据怪物特性考虑出牌策略和使用丹药时机，也是实力的一部分哦。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114500/extras/eddea732baa83d09e71c6b0f82ff768f.poster.avif?t=1669818932\" width=726 height=408 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114500/extras/eddea732baa83d09e71c6b0f82ff768f.webm?t=1669818932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114500/extras/eddea732baa83d09e71c6b0f82ff768f.mp4?t=1669818932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>欢迎一起探讨交流，群：879319038",
